ssets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b1b40370a33956a53658b98f6c866e6a65a99e","tid":1847434,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zEJ8Ur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zEJ8Ur.jpg&h=56dcb446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637eb37aaaf7f3b2555c6aa4ace31e21872e9949","tid":1847434,"uid":162015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bebaa2e21ef3bc3788b9c8c19925a045fa90601e","tid":1847434,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tj1krMW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTj1krMW.png&h=5cd36405&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b5cc6f99fc8c7162eb7fbf54dba2fe7fdcfa68c","tid":1847434,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"Source: 基本上已可斷言武漢肺炎係來自武漢P4實驗室<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846058</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/news.guo.offload.media/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/25133703/Brief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fnews.guo.offload.media%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F25133703%2FBrief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtbz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=de0e888d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/news.guo.offload.media/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/25133703/Brief-summary-of-evidence-of-lab-finish.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n懶人包：<br />\n1. 武漢沙士病毒好可能係人工<br />\n<br />\n-佢同2017年浙江蝙蝠身上發現嘅冠狀病毒嘅E protein 100% 一樣 (相應嘅DNA 相似度都有225/228)，下一隻最接近嘅病毒已經只有低於95%一樣。<br />\n<br />\n病毒嘅基因複制同人類唔同；佢哋冇糾錯機制，發生變異機率相當大。即使E protein為保守序列，病毒品種相對不易產生變異，自然界中仍然非常唔可能有兩種冠狀病毒嘅E protein 完全一樣。SARS唔同亞種嘅E protein都有少量差別。<br />\n<br />\n-ORF8 基因通常病毒品種之間分別好大，2017浙江嗰隻嘅ORF8 同其他冠狀病毒最多只有60%似，但係同武漢沙士就有94.21%一樣<br />\n<br />\n2. 電腦推算武漢沙士病毒入侵人體嘅方式與SARS異常接近<br />\n<br />\nSARS入侵人體第一步，係病毒嘅S protein 痴落人體嘅ACE2 受體. 武漢沙士嘅S protein 整體上同SARS或者2017浙江嗰隻都唔似，但係真正痴落人體嗰部分就同沙士好似。最重要嗰五個氨基酸雖然同沙士有四個唔一樣，但係物理特性相似。電腦分析亦估算武漢沙士同人體ACE2 receptor 親和度非常高，只比SARS略低<br />\n<br />\n所以文章推斷為：有可能係有人參考沙士入侵呼吸道細胞ACE2 受體嘅方法，去改造2017年浙江蝙蝠身上發現嘅冠狀病毒，再放出自然環境（如武漢市場）繁殖一段短時間"},{"pid":"c3fa5bfb44d9173c11f77a338576cd78d275bbc5","tid":1847434,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:44:38.000Z","msg":"前線同線恥笑區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"bebaa2e21ef3bc3788b9c8c19925a045fa90601e","tid":1847434,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tj1krMW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTj1krMW.png&h=5cd36405&s={SIZE}\" />"}}